OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy morning with rain
OL,6,Fspreading to all parts. Turning drier
OL,7,Fin the afternoon, but staying quite
OL,8,Fcloudy in the west with a few showers.
OL,9,FSome afternoon brightness developing
OL,10,Faround Inverness and Nairn. Warm.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRain pushes north through the
OL,13,Fevening, becoming dry for a time
OL,14,Fovernight before more cloud and patchy
OL,15,Flight rain spread into the west
OL,16,Fthrough the early hours.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
