OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FCloudy morning in the west
OL,6,Fwith some light rain, dry and brighter
OL,7,Fin the east. Bright spells and a few
OL,8,Fshowers through the afternoon. Rain in
OL,9,Fthe evening. Warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FMostly
OL,12,Fdry, warm and bright in the east over
OL,13,Fthe weekend and on Monday. Cooler and
OL,14,Fcloudier with rain at times in the
OL,15,Fwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
